missionEventData.data2: In the far reaches of the Outer Rim a rebellion is forming. A rebel cell led by the frigate Redemption and ace pilot Keyan Farlander have been striking back against the evil galactic empire. But the Emperor is at the height of his power, and even now he is marshalling his forces at the edge of the mid-rim. But help has come from the most unlikely of places. The captain of an imperial corvette has sent the rebel freedom fighters a secret message, he wishes to defect...

missionEventData.data1: Warning! Ship emerging from Hyperspace. It's the Invincible!
Red One a group of Tie Bombers are heading for transport group Arroyo. Take them out.
Transport group Arroyo you are cleared for evacuation.
The Corvettes will cover your departure.
There are still Tie Bombers active. Take them out.
Our Corvette Sonnen has been destroyed!
Our Corvette Mahan has been destroyed!

Our analysis of data collected from your reconnaissance mission to Dellalt has confirmed that the Empire is beginning a major offensive in this sector. We believe that their first goal is to destroy our secret base on Briggia. High Command has decided to completely abandon our Briggian base. Your mission is to protect our transports as they make their run to their hyperspace jump points.
Red One another group of Tie Bombers are heading for transport group Phoenix. Take them out.
Transport Group Phoenix you are cleared for departure. Stay clear of the Invincible and we'll keep those fighters off you.
Red One, we need to destroy all Tie Bombers before the next transport group can launch.
They're not giving up. Another group of Bombers is going for Transport group Fondor.
Transport Group Fondor you are cleared for departure. Stay clear of the Invincible and we'll keep those fighters off you.
Red One, we need to destroy all Tie Bombers before the next transport group can launch.
This is Red One. We're on them.
Thanks Red Squadron. More Imperial ships are entering the area. It's time for you to get to the jump point.
